<h1>Getting Started</h1>

<p>
Steps to get started using Open Item Sets:
<ol>
  <li>Register an account!</li>
  <li>Build your own item sets, or browse around and subscribe to ones you like.</li>
  <li>Download our Open Item Sets desktop application (see below) to sync your online item sets to the
  League of Legends client.</li>
</ol>
</p>

<p><strong>Important Note</strong>
Item sets created by Open Item Sets will not show up on the Item Sets tab in the profile window. It is stored seperately and will show
up ingame, so don't worry if it doesn't show up in the game lobby client.
</p>

